---
// Footer override — 3-column grid + Vreko attribution line
---

<footer class="wj-footer">
	<div class="wj-footer__columns">
		<div class="wj-footer__col">
			<p class="wj-footer__col-label">About</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/">What is workspace.json?</a></li>
				<li><a href="/governance/">Governance</a></li>
				<li><a href="/changelog/">Changelog</a></li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://github.com/workspacejson/spec/blob/main/LICENSE" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						License (Apache 2.0)
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="wj-footer__col">
			<p class="wj-footer__col-label">Resources</p>
			<ul>
				<li><a href="/spec/">Spec (latest)</a></li>
				<li><a href="/audit/">Audit Tool</a></li>
				<li><a href="/examples/">Examples</a></li>
				<li><a href="/faq/">FAQ</a></li>
			</ul>
		</div>
		<div class="wj-footer__col">
			<p class="wj-footer__col-label">Project</p>
			<ul>
				<li>
					<a href="https://github.com/workspacejson/spec" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						GitHub
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/agents-audit" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						npm: agents-audit
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@workspacejson/spec" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						npm: @workspacejson/spec
					</a>
				</li>
				<li>
					<a href="https://www.npmjs.com/package/@workspacejson/rules" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">
						npm: @workspacejson/rules
					</a>
				</li>
			</ul>
		</div>
	</div>
	<p class="wj-footer__attribution">
		Initial spec authored and maintained by the team at
		<a href="https://vreko.dev" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">vreko.dev</a>.
		workspace.json is licensed under Apache 2.0 and proposed for AAIF donation.
	</p>
</footer>

<style>
	.wj-footer {
		border-top: 1px solid var(--sl-color-hairline, var(--sl-color-gray-2));
		padding: 2.5rem 0 1.5rem;
		margin-top: 4rem;
	}

	.wj-footer__columns {
		display: grid;
		grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
		gap: 2rem;
		max-width: var(--sl-content-width, 52rem);
		margin: 0 auto;
		padding: 0 1rem;
	}

	.wj-footer__col-label {
		font-size: 0.6875rem;
		font-weight: 700;
		text-transform: uppercase;
		letter-spacing: 0.08em;
		color: var(--sl-color-accent);
		margin: 0 0 0.75rem;
	}

	.wj-footer__col ul {
		list-style: none;
		padding: 0;
		margin: 0;
		display: flex;
		flex-direction: column;
		gap: 0.5rem;
	}

	.wj-footer__col a {
		font-size: 0.875rem;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
		text-decoration: none;
	}

	.wj-footer__col a:hover {
		color: var(--sl-color-accent);
	}

	.wj-footer__attribution {
		text-align: center;
		margin-top: 2rem;
		padding: 0 1rem;
		font-size: 0.8125rem;
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
		max-width: var(--sl-content-width, 52rem);
		margin-left: auto;
		margin-right: auto;
	}

	.wj-footer__attribution a {
		color: var(--sl-color-gray-4);
		text-decoration: underline;
		text-decoration-color: var(--sl-color-hairline, var(--sl-color-gray-3));
	}

	.wj-footer__attribution a:hover {
		color: var(--sl-color-accent);
	}

	@media (max-width: 640px) {
		.wj-footer__columns {
			grid-template-columns: 1fr;
			gap: 1.5rem;
		}
	}
</style>
